PN,39101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779703923
OL,3,CMen shot and injured in 'targeted'
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FTwo men have been wounded after being
OL,7,Fshot in what police believe was a
OL,8,Ftargeted attack in the town of Prescot
OL,9,Fon Merseyside.
OL,11,FThe men, both in their 20s, were found
OL,12,Fwith gunshot wounds on Pottery Lane,
OL,13,Fnext to Stadt Moers Park, just before
OL,14,F3pm on Sunday.
OL,16,FBoth are in hospital and Merseyside
OL,17,FPolice have urged people to avoid the
OL,18,Farea while they investigate.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
