FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779703923
OL,3,CMen shot and injured in 'targeted'
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Paul Speight
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement: "To fire a weapon
OL,8,Fin our communities at any time is of
OL,9,Fcourse a concern, but to do so in a
OL,10,Fresidential area on a Sunday afternoon
OL,11,Fis beyond comprehension."
OL,13,FGun crime has become "increasingly
OL,14,Frare" in Merseyside in recent years,
OL,15,Fhe added.
OL,17,FThis has been "in no small part down
OL,18,Fto the information, engagement and
OL,19,Fpartnership work in those areas which
OL,20,Fhave been affected", Mr Speight said
OL,21,Fas he appealed for information.
OL,26,@sD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779703923
OL,3,CMen shot and injured in 'targeted'
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"If you know anything, speak to us
OL,7,Fdirectly or anonymously and we will
OL,8,Ftake positive action to find and
OL,9,Fremove from the community any firearms
OL,10,Fand those people reckless enough to
OL,11,Fuse them."
OL,13,FMr Speight added: "Our initial
OL,14,Fassessment is this was a targeted
OL,15,Fattack on the two victims, for reasons
OL,16,Fwe will establish as the investigation
OL,17,Fprogresses.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779703923
OL,3,CMen shot and injured in 'targeted'
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,F"I want to make it clear to anyone
OL,7,Finvolved that our determination to
OL,8,Ffind those responsible will be
OL,9,Fabsolute, and we will target anyone
OL,10,Fwho has carried out this shooting, or
OL,11,Fassisted those responsible in any way."
OL,13,FA woman who lives opposite the cordon
OL,14,Fon Pottery Lane said: "Where do they
OL,15,Feven get guns from? It's so quiet and
OL,16,Fpeaceful around here. There's just
OL,17,Fthree houses on our street. I hope the
OL,18,Fyoung boys are ok."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1779703923
OL,3,CMen shot and injured in 'targeted'
OL,4,Cattack
OL,6,FAnother neighbour said: "My
OL,7,Fgrandchildren were in their bedroom
OL,8,Fand shouted me saying grandma come and
OL,9,Fsee this. We saw the helicopter land
OL,10,Fthen all the police tape went up.
OL,12,F"I didn't know what happened. It's
OL,13,Fshocking, it's the middle of the day
OL,14,Fon a sunny bank holiday. There's kids
OL,15,Fand dog walkers always in that park
OL,16,Fand people are running around with
OL,17,Fguns."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
